"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-simone-biles-conquers-the-vault-third-gold-medal-of-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Even Simone Biles sometimes gets caught up in the legend of Simone Biles.\\u00c2 As she stood atop the podium during Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s vault final, preparing to unleash the flips that would earn her her third gold medal of these Olympics and her 10th overall, her coach Laurent Landi signaled to her:Wait.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurent Landi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurent_Landi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even Simone Biles\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 27}, {\"ngram\": \"the legend\", \"from\": 56, \"to\": 66}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Biles\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 82}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 83, \"to\": 84}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 113}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s vault final\", \"from\": 121, \"to\": 145}, {\"ngram\": \"the flips\", \"from\": 168, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"her her third gold medal\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cObviously once you get up there, your adrenaline is pumping,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said afterward.\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your adrenaline\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe wanted to make sure that I was staying calm and going on my own time, even though the thing said GO and everybody started cheering.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d As she has all Olympics, Biles blocked out the expectations of others and focused on her own.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GO_Transit\", \"score\": 0.999935952692091, \"rank\": 6.404792038565845e-05, \"text\": \"GO\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GO_Transit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GO_Transit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cHe\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 399}, {\"ngram\": \"my own time\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"all Olympics\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"the expectations\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took a breath and began sprinting down the runway.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a breath\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"the runway\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 683}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she landed the Yurchenko double pike vault that bears her name\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the Biles II, one of five eponymous skills\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094it was all but over.\\u00c2 She sealed gold with a less complicated vault that made her combined score a preposterous 15.300.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 705, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"double pike vault\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"name\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the Biles II\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"five eponymous skills\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094it\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 She\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"a less complicated vault\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"her combined score\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Rebeca Andrade, the best gymnast on earth not named Biles, and the 2023 world champion in the vault, finished second with a score of 14.966.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best gymnast\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"earth\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 world champion\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jade Carey, who has spent the past three years reliving the instant when she stumbled on the runway in Tokyo and finished last in this event, took bronze.\\u00c2 Biles hadlamented Andrade\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s skillsafter Thursday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s individual all-around final, saying, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to compete with Rebeca no more!\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1073, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999990714059, \"rank\": 9.241760567080606e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past three years\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the instant\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the runway\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Biles\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"Rebeca\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m tired!\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s way too close.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d On Saturday, after Andrade\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s first vault, Biles turned to Carey, grinned and shrugged dramatically, as if to say, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhat are we supposed to do about her?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d But Biles, 27, had already done what she needed to do, and everyone in Bercy Arena knew it.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.444411560226187e-17, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}, {\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bercy Arena\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Accor_Arena\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"Andrade\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"first vault\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhat\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"her?\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her difficulty score is so high that as long as she stays on her feet, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s almost impossible for anyone else to match her.\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her difficulty score\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"her feet\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrade actually executed her vaults better, by more than two-tenths of a point, but it didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t matter.\\u00c2 This was Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fourth Yurchenko double pike in competition this week\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094once in the qualifiers,once in the team final,once in the individual all-around\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and she said she would be retiring the skill.\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI mean, I kind of nailed that one,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said with a grin.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8574740460528046e-16, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 1923, \"end\": 1932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her vaults\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"more than two-tenths\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1958}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifiers\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"around\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the skill\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"a grin\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As for herself, she was less decisive.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNever say never,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNever\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe next Olympics is at home, so you never know.\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe next Olympics\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2265, \"to\": 2269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am getting really old.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d As she has all week, Biles set records in both age and decoration: She became the oldest woman to win gold in the vault since Ekaterina Kalinchuk, representing the Soviet Union, did so at 30 in 1952, the first time women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gymnastics were contested at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ekaterina_Kalinchuk\", \"score\": 0.9999998259695682, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ekaterina Kalinchuk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ekaterina_Kalinchuk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ekaterina_Kalinchuk\"}, {\"begin\": 2494, \"end\": 2499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999998167368, \"rank\": 1.830826752054851e-10, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"both age\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"decoration\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest woman\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gold today, her second on vault after she also won in Rio, tied her with runner Allyson Felix for second most golds by a U.S. woman.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2659, \"end\": 2662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998085514, \"rank\": 1.9155463667647907e-10, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2685, \"end\": 2698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allyson Felix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allyson_Felix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gold\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"vault\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"second most golds\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"a U.S. woman\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Swimmers Jenny Thompson and Katie Ledecky each have eight.)\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 2767, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles also now owns 40 Olympic and world championship medals, 30 of them gold.\\u00c2 Although Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s vaults were smooth, the process of getting there was not.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"40 Olympic and world championship medals\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s vaults\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tokyo, it was on the vault, of course, that the twisties that had dogged her for weeks became insurmountable.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999990714059, \"rank\": 9.241760567080606e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2989}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisties\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She fell out of her vault\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094an Amanar, which entails two and a half twists\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094during the team final and withdrew from event after event before stripping the twisting elements from her balance beam routine and gutting out a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3104, \"end\": 3110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.410891475811783e-75, \"text\": \"Amanar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"the twisting elements\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3246}, {\"ngram\": \"her balance beam routine\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze medal\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took a year off from practicing and two off from competition before returning in 2023, and she initially performed the Amanar again, but she scrapped it in favor of the Biles II, which has two flips but no twists.\\u00c2 That was at Landi\\u00e2\\u0080